173\t**以便** 回顾之前的聊天内容。\n   174\t\n   175\t#### 验收标准\n   176\t> 
以上验收标准的完整 Gherkin 用例详见 `tests/bdd/im.feature`。\n   177\t\n   178\t
```gherkin\n   179\tFeature: Message History\n   180\t  Scenario: User loads his
torical messages\n   181\t    Given Alice and Bob have exchanged 50 messages\n  
182\t    When Alice opens the conversation\n   183\t    Then the app should load
